Garcés ( 2002 )
reported the occurrence of
Ptychophallus tristani
(as
Pseudothelphusa tristani
) from the San Félix River basin (Chiriquí Province, Panamá ), but we were not able to confirm the identification of the specimens as they are no longer extant (H.A. Garcés, pers. comm. to CM). Another unconfirmed record of
